{"tid":424529,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人感覺人愈大，時間就過得愈快","createTime":"2017-10-04T19:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T09:39:54.000Z","uid":60120,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9279b93e16e9f7539e36d64a3297e34ad329b6ed","tid":424529,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪每個人都一樣啦<br />\n以前仲係細路個時會認為自己係15分鐘內可以做好多野<br />\n讀數秒針慢到想訓教<br />\n想做咩就做咩，因為做極都仲未夠鐘訓教<br />\n<br />\n但依家好似貶個眼就無啦啦過左幾分鐘咁<br />\n做少少野以為唔洗用太多時間，點知做完望番個鐘，會比想像中用多左好多既時間<br />\n人大左，每秒都好似比印象中短左好多咁<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似或者同樣既感覺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284e2bfbb0c48446edcd0875a20caf1589b0e0e0","tid":424529,"uid":81863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:13:48.000Z","msg":"中學六年生涯好似好漫長咁 但一畢業出黎做野 一眨眼就過左六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6aa1196b1925b508202675c15fa78e6b6e5fa6","tid":424529,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23cf7f83a2aef551a9205556759974099bbf5b8c","tid":424529,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:15:31.000Z","msg":"中學果陣18好似好遙遠<br />\n依家我再過多幾年就3字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望番轉頭好似早幾日咁"},{"pid":"f6bb7ff6c31068317666b35af902baeaf63993f2","tid":424529,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:28:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.exactlywhatistime.com/psychology-of-time/time-perception/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.exactlywhatistime.com%2Fpsychology-of-time%2Ftime-perception%2F&d=xLLvEgZW%2BA57V9waaKmN4pzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=622ac9a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.exactlywhatistime.com/psychology-of-time/time-perception/</a></blockquote><br />\n原本我都有諗過係心理/個人因素<br />\n但我個人既體驗係，當自己讀數秒數時<br />\n細個個時係會成日數太快，一秒前已經數定<br />\n大個左會反而數太慢，會比秒針追過<br />\n如果以語速做標準既話，大個左讀數好似好急咁<br />\n但細個個時係每秒都等得好辛苦既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d00f8ae838b675fab515003d91ddec980dda19e","tid":424529,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 原本我都有諗過係心理/個人因素<br />\n但我個人既體驗係，當自己讀數秒數時<br />\n細個個時係會成日數太快，一秒前已經數定<br />\n大個左會反而數太慢，會比秒針追過<br />\n如果以語速做標準既話，大個左讀數好似好急咁<br />\n但細個個時係每秒都等得好辛苦既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠立體"},{"pid":"7df4b9293e3b91c8ee80472c1d3c27eb38e63fcd","tid":424529,"uid":55151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:36:15.000Z","msg":"正常 思想唔同左 責任大左"},{"pid":"30f908a3ba32a4e374b85fb0cf6d27e0645be5b1","tid":424529,"uid":134335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"有 好似有幻覺定細個專注好多<br />\n成日覺得明明好短時間嘅嘢最後用多好多時間<br />\n覺得細個嘅15分鐘=依家30分鐘on99"},{"pid":"d1e23aa15542b68c5691400f0f00a9b7392d4f4d","tid":424529,"uid":93132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T20:04:36.000Z","msg":"記得當天一起唱着告別校園時 那些愉快動人琴聲仍像奏到面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afef92bbeb407467ab8b3a361aea494cf81c5e82","tid":424529,"uid":129922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"有2個講法<br />\n<br />\n1. 時間壓縮左， 以前的24小時， 現在只有18小時<br />\n<br />\n2. 多左上網， 智能手機， 無聊時多左方法解悶， 時間自然易過好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過真的不想長大， 責任大左， 壓力大左， 笑容都少左"},{"pid":"fe7a176e93e0fe10d99a4be115b49cbbe9737aba","tid":424529,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:14:40.000Z","msg":"因為個腦慢左"},{"pid":"3666626b25ee9ba37bcd96e4bf1339a95199a667","tid":424529,"uid":70527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:20:00.000Z","msg":"你兩歲過一年就已經要體驗多過往既一半時間<br />\n你一百歲過一年就只係體驗左1%"},{"pid":"207bb404f7f729cbafbc1ae45df3924d856cbef4","tid":424529,"uid":151506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:31:07.000Z","msg":"人愈大d時間再唔係自己，特別返工之後時間永遠唔夠用，好似d 時間飛得好快咁。<br />\n<br />\n以前讀書有好多時間做其他野，覺得有好多時間用，所以覺得好慢。"},{"pid":"3522e36c7ec3324ecace0663c6814f02b760d1ad","tid":424529,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:40:32.000Z","msg":"覺得個腦冇細個轉得咁快<br />\n腦轉得越來越慢<br />\n時間過得越來越快<br />\n好快又一日<br />\n好快又死"},{"pid":"f94424577a2e6ee426aa3c6f3c3c646e5ac2ed90","tid":424529,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:27:27.000Z","msg":"細個返學啲時間過好耐<br />\n依家返工眨下眼就一年<br />\n時間真係唔等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36dc664e21b8d97053cafa70ecbdfd94b1165d37","tid":424529,"uid":76379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你兩歲過一年就已經要體驗多過往既一半時間<br />\n你一百歲過一年就只係體驗左1%</blockquote><br />\n我記得把李笑來本《把時間當作朋友》呢本都係咁講"}]}